com.example.foodtracker3

Class Product

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.foodtracker3.Product
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Product objects are tied to entries in the database. Product objects are used to work with UI, and contain all the necessary information to update entries in the database. Implements Serializable so the class can be compatible with Bundles
    Version:
    1.0.0 Jun 7, 2020
    Author:
    Andrew Dineen, Aidan Fallstorm, Rick Patneaude, Eli Storlie, Marco Villafana
    See Also:
